3px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-13_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-14_"><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-127_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-126_"><span style="font-weight: 700;">Need your bike fixed within 1 hours? We say yes!<br>Combining motorbike and ebike? We say yes!<br>The toughest cases most bike shops can't handle? We say yes!<br>Craving a cup of coffee? The answer is always yes and enjoy it!</span></span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-124_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-123_">Step into the world of Espresso Bicycle Repair, located on Lockwood Ridge Rd in Sarasota, where the name itself holds a double meaning. For owner Hugo Rodriguez, it signifies the promise that if your bike breaks down, worry not – while you enjoy a cup of coffee, he may already have it fixed. Moreover, just like an espresso shot, Hugo aims to provide lightning-fast "Quick Bicycle Repair" services, ensuring a 24-hour turnaround time. His passion for coffee reflects the start of an invigorating day, much like his dedication to efficient bike repairs.&nbsp;</span></p><div title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg1" class="sc-TBWPX ebxtzr pf-24_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_2.jpg?v=1691117152" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_2.jpg?v=1691117152 1536w" width="4096" height="3312" alt="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida"/></div><div title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg1-mb" class="sc-TBWPX ebxtzr pf-25_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_2.jpg?v=1691117152" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_2.jpg?v=1691117152 1536w" width="4096" height="3312" alt="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida"/></div><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-18_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-20_">In Hugo's vision, customers should <b>"Ride the bike, stop in my shop, have a cup of coffee, and keep riding."</b> This means that if you go to visit his store to test ride the Urtopia Carbon 1s, you'll be treated to a free, delicious coffee – an extra gift exclusively for Urtopians haha.</span></p><a href="/pages/test-ride?name=Espresso%20Bicycle%20Repairs" target="_self" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-ksdxgE kPRAAR pf-139_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-138_">Book a Free Test Ride</span></a><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-133_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-132_">It's All About Love and Hard Work</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-130_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-129_">Hugo boasts two decades of experience in the bike industry, with a professional background in bicycle mechanisms and bike fitting. His journey in the cycling world has been nothing short of extraordinary, from starting as a skilled bike technician to managing several bike shops. In his own words, "I am always extremely competitive," and he firmly believes that competitiveness breeds creativity. It's this drive that led him to elevate a shop's revenue by a staggering 200% in only 1 year during his tenure as a manager, consistently surpassing people's expectations because he knows how to value himself.<br><br>Beyond the bike world, Hugo is a family hero, determined to provide a better life for his loved ones. Starting as a humble bike assistant two decades ago, he always knew what he truly wanted – a life guided by two core beliefs: "love and hard work." Love has been his anchor throughout his 20-year journey in the bike industry, transitioning from a passionate road bike racer since middle school to embracing cycling as a way of life, ensuring he stays healthy and invigorated every day. Riding has long been integrated into his life.</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-148_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-147_"><span style="font-weight: 700;">"Cycling means living, like freedom coming to me with joy.”</span></span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-136_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-135_">But it is Hugo's unwavering commitment to hard work that sets him apart. With a wealth of knowledge that surpasses most bike shop technicians, he fearlessly accepts challenging repair orders and masterfully completes each case with remarkable efficiency.</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-142_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-141_">Urtopia and Espresso</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-145_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-144_">Hugo's journey with Urtopia began during his previous managerial role, where Urtopia always took center stage in his shop, capturing the attention of passersby. With Urtopia earning high praise from owners, Hugo was convinced that collaborating with the brand was the right choice.<br><br>"Reasonable price and perfect business model" – Hugo's encounter with numerous ebikes left him astonished by the standout features of Urtopia Carbon 1s. With its carbon frame, GPS, fingerprint technology, Bluetooth music, navigation, and voice control, Urtopia defied expectations, offering a level of technology and innovation usually seen in $5000+ bikes. In a place like Florida, where ebike popularity and a love for cutting-edge tech reign, Hugo was convinced that Urtopia Carbon 1s embodies the perfect business model for marketing.</span></p><a href="/pages/test-ride?name=Espresso%20Bicycle%20Repairs" target="_self" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-ksdxgE kPRAAR pf-21_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-23_">Book a Free Test Ride</span></a><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-26_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-28_">The Answer is Always Yes</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-29_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-31_">For Urtopia users in Sarasota, they are in for a treat with Espresso Bicycle Repair's exceptional after-sales service, summed up in three points:&nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-15_ pf-gs-paragraph-2 Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-17_"><span style="font-weight: 700;">"Always yes, 24-hour turnaround, detail-oriented.”</span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e352" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-32_"><div style="--cw:893px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-33_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-34_"><div title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg2" class="sc-TBWPX ebxtzr pf-35_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_3.jpg?v=1691117152" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_3.jpg?v=1691117152 1536w" width="4096" height="3504" alt="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida"/></div><div title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg2-mb" class="sc-TBWPX ebxtzr pf-36_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_3.jpg?v=1691117152" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/files/Untitled_3.jpg?v=1691117152 1536w" width="4096" height="3504" alt="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida" title="Urtopia store in Sarasota Florida"/></div><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-37_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-39_">In Hugo's world, the word "NO" is almost unheard of. With his 20 years of experience in the bike industry and an unwavering commitment to hard work, he and his team have earned a reputation for impeccable bike repairs. They can complete complex cases, such as fixing a broken and completely apart bike frame, in just 3 hours. They even took on a challenging hybrid of half ebike, half motorbike – showcasing their brilliance in repairs. When asked about their secret, Hugo simply said, "Say yes to anything and focus on finding solutions."<br><br>Hugo's insistence on a 24-hour turnaround stems from his desire to avoid keeping customers waiting for days. He values efficiency and believes in making things simple. Hand over your bike today, and Hugo will have it fixed by today. Often, they manage to repair a bike within just an hour.<br><br>If you think that Espresso Bicycle Repair's speed might compromise quality and attention to detail, think again. Quality and detail-oriented work are their priority, a treasure gained from 20 years of professional knowledge. Ensuring customers receive the perfect repair is of utmost importance to them.<br><br>If you reside in Sarasota, visit Espresso Bicycle Repair, enjoy a cup of coffee, and test ride the Urtopia Carbon 1s for an unparalleled cycling experience. And if you decide to purchase the Carbon 1s, you can rest assured you'll receive top-notch after-sales service. Just like an espresso, the shop embodies the essence of both deliciousness and efficiency, symbolizing quality and excellence.</span></p><a href="/pages/test-ride?name=Espresso%